Following Project fetches images data from https://api.flickr.com/services/rest/

1.Libraries used - Retrofit , Picasso , chuck , retrofit converter
2.Architecture Used - MVP.

Implementation - Search bar is being used to search any query.As soon as you start search ,api call
                 is created to fetch images corresponding to the query you have used.

                 Pagination : 10 items are being fetched in one api call.As soon scroll is at last
                              position ,we are fetching the items of next page.



Improvements -  Architecture improvemntents,UNIT Test cases